{
  "stem": "4187.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Things like-- what I'm trying to say is that something incredibly positive had to happen, which was entirely out of your hands.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You could not make anything happen.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It had to happen through fate.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "How is it ever going to happen?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the realization again and again and again that you are in the hands of these-- I won't say beasts, because I don't want to hurt the animals-- of these things, these things who've got power over you 100%.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there you are in your-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] --short cover-up, at their mercy, as they want it.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I can't-- I've never been able to explain what it's like, and I believe that nobody can.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I suppose the difference, in a sense, in a sense-- the difference between talking about it and listening to it and it happening would be if you see an incredibly well-painted picture where, let's say fire-- you look at it and you think, this is real.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But you touch it, and then you put your hand in the fire, in the real fire, and you'll know the difference.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So one cannot-- it is not possible, because the suffering is so-- it's so psychological.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The cold doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The hunger doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The thirst doesn't matter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's this unbelievable terror that matters, where you just don't know what's going to happen to you next second.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You really didn't know, because you may have been perfectly all right and walking next to a barrack, and the German would come and-- and hit you with a whip.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it might hit you on the head and you're gone, or your eyes are gone, and then you're gone, of course.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You just didn't know which second is going to bring what.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
